gov.nih.nlm.meme
Interface Initializable

All Known Subinterfaces:
MEMERequestListener, ServerThread
All Known Implementing Classes:
HTTPRequestListener, MEMESchedule, MIDDataSourcePool, MRDDataSourcePool, SessionTimeoutThread, ThreadPool
public interface Initializable

Generically allows an application to give components known to require initialization an opportunity to do so before normal application processing proceeds. In this model, the application itself must implement InitializationContext.

Author:
MEME Group
